{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_码头选择",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·码头捞箱（A跳水/B喊价/C看热闹）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_码头",
              "state": "resolved",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "洋船还泊在那点。码头的热闹散了，热闹留下的话头才刚开始长牙。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "箱子还在水里扑腾着冒泡。埃德加的「Ten DOLLARS!」悬在半空，人群的眼神发烫——可没一个人动。",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a_tiao",
          "text": "〔跳水捞箱〕脱了褂子就往下扎",
          "next": "a_1"
        },
        {
          "id": "b_han",
          "text": "〔当中间人〕「十块大洋哪个信哦！先把定钱亮出来——老子给你们喊人下水！」",
          "next": "b_1"
        },
        {
          "id": "c_kan",
          "text": "〔看热闹〕抱着胳膊往后站站",
          "next": "c_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "a_1": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_码头选择",
            "signal": "dock_chose_a"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "startWaterMinigame",
          "params": {
            "id": "dock_crate_tutorial"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_2"
    },
    "a_2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "playSfx",
          "params": {
            "id": "sfx_underwater_grab"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_3"
    },
    "a_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "摸到箱子那一刻——脚腕猛地被拽了一下。黑浑的水里什么都看不见，只有那一下，又冷又实。",
      "next": "a_4"
    },
    "a_4": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "playSignalCue",
          "params": {
            "id": "axiu_faint"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_5"
    },
    "a_5": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "showOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "ankle_scratch",
            "image": "ankle_scratch",
            "xPercent": 50,
            "yPercent": 48,
            "widthPercent": 52
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_6"
    },
    "a_6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他侥幸上了岸。手腕上多了几道抓痕——又细又深，水底下，不该有这种来源。",
      "next": "a_7"
    },
    "a_7": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "hideOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "ankle_scratch"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "showOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "compass_silver_map_book",
            "image": "compass_silver_map_book",
            "xPercent": 50,
            "yPercent": 47,
            "widthPercent": 60
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_8"
    },
    "a_8": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "箱子开了：一只指针乱转的罗盘。几页手绘地图碎片——上头标着「神仙顶」「阎王岭」，旁边一行行洋文批注。还有一摞线装风水古籍的复印件，和一张洋婆子的照片。",
      "next": "a_9"
    },
    "a_9": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（罗盘乱转必撞煞……洋人研究勒个整啥子？）",
      "next": "a_10"
    },
    "a_10": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "hideOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "compass_silver_map_book"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_11"
    },
    "a_11": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "埃德加"
      },
      "text": "Good job！说好的十块大洋——呃，box 进了水，货损了 value……（从兜里摸出两枚银角子塞过来）辛苦费！Very 慷慨！",
      "next": "a_12"
    },
    "a_12": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveItem",
          "params": {
            "id": "silver_dimes",
            "count": 2
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 4
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "a_13"
    },
    "a_13": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "两枚银角子？！你龟儿管这叫十块大洋？！……算咯，洋人这笔账，比僵尸还邪门。",
      "next": "a_14"
    },
    "a_14": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一旁的克拉拉没看箱子。她盯着他手腕上那几道抓痕，皱了皱眉——没说话。心里记了一笔。",
      "next": "n_end_flags"
    },
    "b_1": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_码头选择",
            "signal": "dock_chose_b"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "b_2"
    },
    "b_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他往人群前头一站，嗓门一扯，三句话把价钱从十块「大洋」砍成了看得见摸得着的几串铜钱，又把两个会水的脚夫推下了水。",
      "next": "b_3"
    },
    "b_3": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 8
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "b_4"
    },
    "b_4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "箱子捞上来，他抽了头钱。远远地，他瞥见开箱时露出的物件——罗盘、地图、一摞旧书。地图上有两个他认得的地名：神仙顶。阎王岭。",
      "next": "b_5"
    },
    "b_5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "克拉拉把这个会来事的本地人上下打量了一遍，在小本子上记了点什么。",
      "next": "n_end_flags"
    },
    "c_1": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_码头选择",
            "signal": "dock_chose_c"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "c_2"
    },
    "c_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他抱着胳膊看完了全场：有人下水，箱子捞起，洋人掏钱比掏心还慢。热闹散场，各回各家。",
      "next": "c_3"
    },
    "c_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "当晚茶馆里，箱子里的物件已经被传得有鼻子有眼——罗盘、洋文地图，还有人赌咒发誓说看见了「神仙顶」三个字。",
      "next": "n_end_flags"
    },
    "n_end_flags": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_码头选择",
            "signal": "dock_resolved"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}